{"type":"article","id":3987,"title":"和三十年前的对比","uid":11157,"topics":[],"contents":"三十年前六月份的北京，大陆人有难，香港人毫不犹豫地支援：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQO-LHLD5Bg9weKjHNDrldINjqPYiPr_hkTILhgsi4U_YhZG5cf\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQO-LHLD5Bg9weKjHNDrldINjqPYiPr_hkTILhgsi4U_YhZG5cf\" alt=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcQO-LHLD5Bg9weKjHNDrldINjqPYiPr_hkTILhgsi4U_YhZG5cf\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.ibb.co/8PMM6XJ/Bocdqvo-IQAAN4mt.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/8PMM6XJ/Bocdqvo-IQAAN4mt.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.ibb.co/8PMM6XJ/Bocdqvo-IQAAN4mt.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.ibb.co/qgG49bs/101856001-454875cd-97ab-4be5-ad48-9baee0bbcaa4.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qgG49bs/101856001-454875cd-97ab-4be5-ad48-9baee0bbcaa4.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.ibb.co/qgG49bs/101856001-454875cd-97ab-4be5-ad48-9baee0bbcaa4.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n然而三十年后的今天，到了危难的关头，你们等来的却是：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.ibb.co/KmNC1vk/img-0834725f95102a14f28a698239e37e22.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/KmNC1vk/img-0834725f95102a14f28a698239e37e22.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.ibb.co/KmNC1vk/img-0834725f95102a14f28a698239e37e22.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.ibb.co/cF7WtwS/img-034e81e3b41f731d19a5aefbd47b0dad.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/cF7WtwS/img-034e81e3b41f731d19a5aefbd47b0dad.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.ibb.co/cF7WtwS/img-034e81e3b41f731d19a5aefbd47b0dad.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.ibb.co/XSxc01C/img-457db13b956a8aec5797831cdeecb21a.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/XSxc01C/img-457db13b956a8aec5797831cdeecb21a.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.ibb.co/XSxc01C/img-457db13b956a8aec5797831cdeecb21a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n真的很想替大陆人说一声对不起，抱歉。但希望你们不要错怪我们，我们也只是被支配着思考，被支配着生活。但愿有一天，我们会从长睡中醒来。","date":"2019-08-24","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}